\begin_layout Remark
The derivative of a test function is a test function; so is the sum of two
 test functions, as well as scalar multiples of test functions.
 
\series bold
Thus, the set of test functions forms a vector space; we call it 
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

