\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Remark
Let 
\begin_inset Formula $F$
\end_inset

 be a test function and let 
\begin_inset Formula $\phi$
\end_inset

 be a weakly increasing function.
 Then
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
G\left(x\right):=F\left(x\right)\phi\left(x\right)
\]

\end_inset

